## Why a Travel Credit Card?

Travel credit cards aren't just about earning miles—they unlock premium experiences: airport lounge access, free checked bags, travel insurance, and annual travel credits that can offset (or eliminate) annual fees.

The average traveler who flies 4+ times per year can recoup hundreds to thousands in value through the right card.

## Best Travel Credit Cards 2026

### 1. Chase Sapphire Reserve®

